## Utilities
# help: [A] `sbrc` - Source the .bashrc file
alias sbrc='source ~/.bashrc'
# help: [A] `obrc` - Open the .bashrc file in vim
alias obrc='vim ~/.bashrc'
# help: [A] `ocd` - Open the current directory
alias ocd='explorer .'

